{"tid":729510,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Verbatim係咪已經打遍天下冇敵手？","createTime":"2018-07-04T15:13:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-08T19:21:50.000Z","uid":86378,"like":15,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"69ea098efbdda7a3b72d443b2c9231a53e297bc4","tid":729510,"uid":86378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T15:13:01.000Z","msg":"用個好多唔同牌子嘅電話配件，都係Verbatim最可靠。<br />\n以前以為xPower掂，點知原來狗也不屌，連爛兩條線。<br />\n而家插頭尿袋線乜都係Verbatim, 未壞過。"},{"pid":"887587160a9d2ed28cb95ea2e957103980668259","tid":729510,"uid":192670,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T15:19:09.000Z","msg":"我買左條2米iPhone 線...用唔夠2個月GGed...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f140c423fcabdb028c6fc42082fce3b5ed51f59","tid":729510,"uid":16904,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T15:20:32.000Z","msg":"Xpower根本就係垃圾"},{"pid":"29e6f45bf5a6422a7d4cdbcb074bd625364261d2","tid":729510,"uid":13653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T15:21:52.000Z","msg":"兩三年前買佢條叉電線，好撚正，又叉得快，又有金屬外層，養兔仔都唔驚咬爛"},{"pid":"ba7ce0137baeb691afa3afbccae86d72c8f8e59a","tid":729510,"uid":407,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T15:24:11.000Z","msg":"有條verbatim 2 in 1 lightning + micro usb, 已經爛左好多次, 個lightning 接口留左係機身, 同條線分離左, 不過好彩有保養, 但係隔一兩個月上去換一次都好煩<br />\n<br />\n但係其他就咁lightning/ micro usb 就幾好"},{"pid":"56db5d65bb6e792e6735ab803fc5a34e5dba0f21","tid":729510,"uid":86378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba7ce0137baeb691afa3afbccae86d72c8f8e59a","tid":729510,"uid":407,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T15:24:11.000Z","msg":"有條verbatim 2 in 1 lightning + micro usb, 已經爛左好多次, 個lightning 接口留左係機身, 同條線分離左, 不過好彩有保養, 但係隔一兩個月上去換一次都好煩<br />\n<br />\n但係其他就咁lightning/ micro usb 就幾好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T15:25:20.000Z","msg":"我都諗緊買唔買果條2in1/3in1<br />\n咁就算了"},{"pid":"f66fc36aa30f985d6fc0cdd2ed0a764f727f7f94","tid":729510,"uid":9098,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T15:55:45.000Z","msg":"用過幾條但唔知點解壞過兩條lighting線，<br />\n唔係條線斷/爛，但係好快接觸不良，<br />\n明明擺係屋企無屈住佢都壞咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n反而有條舊xpower Android線可能少用，<br />\n用咗幾年都仲用到，係個樣殘哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家用緊另外一款唔知咩野牌子既線，<br />\n好似日文字咁既，價錢貴唔過上面兩款但幾好用、無壞無盛又叉得幾快<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfea6531b0a4f3b09e5476cca7eb4053c2bd6d49","tid":729510,"uid":9098,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T15:57:06.000Z","msg":"唔係話有保養唔好，<br />\n只係我諗唔少人都覺得花時間專登走去換過條，<br />\n可能行過街隨手買返條仲快手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef84368f49b4bbfb326470b9e1f5357905f51e04","tid":729510,"uid":27108,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T16:26:36.000Z","msg":"Verbatim質素係唔錯<br />\n但係唔夠跟貼潮流<br />\nLightning線得usb2.0速度<br />\n得2.4a冇pd<br />\n亦冇type c to lightning<br />\n<br />\n最近轉左ego<br />\n有type c to lightning <br />\n有pd +usb 3.0<br />\n仲有跟魔術貼可以隨時札住條線<br />\n<br />\n利申 非打手"},{"pid":"eca2c8431b127f437393ae97b7e5100d0789f7f9","tid":729510,"uid":26167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T16:51:55.000Z","msg":"完全無研究<br />\n正話係街急用求其買左個尿袋就係呢個牌子<br />\n8000 mah<br />\n有咩特別咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d129b8893a2e3699d8683d9f8c102decf90c3ac0","tid":729510,"uid":23677,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T17:01:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">xpower幾時有掂過？</span></span>"},{"pid":"2cad17d36303bd35ff640a861028631921881111","tid":729510,"uid":35660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T17:09:12.000Z","msg":"尿袋正呀"},{"pid":"adfb508dc6dedc8c9d4c85b04862f02765cc1193","tid":729510,"uid":35021,"like":2,"dislike":2,"